39:24.362 --> 39:25.613
It held up well.

39:25.613 --> 39:26.739
I like that you did Damascus.

39:26.739 --> 39:27.907
I like the pattern of it.

39:27.907 --> 39:29.242
It's really pretty.

39:29.242 --> 39:30.702
Overall, well done.

39:30.702 --> 39:34.581
- Thank you.

39:34.581 --> 39:36.249
- All right, gentlemen.

39:36.249 --> 39:37.375
To test the sharpness
