39:46.551 --> 39:49.137
- I'm ready.

39:49.804 --> 39:56.769
<i>♪ ♪</i>

40:02.442 --> 40:04.110
- All right, Josh.

40:04.110 --> 40:05.403
These are sharp.

40:05.403 --> 40:07.113
You can see these cuts,

40:07.113 --> 40:10.033
just clean rakes
across the chest.

40:10.033 --> 40:13.661
No tearing. I actually like
that hook you've got.

40:13.661 --> 40:15.622
These are definitely cutters.
Nicely done.

40:15.622 --> 40:17.540
- Thank you.
- All right, Chad, you're up.

40:17.540 --> 40:18.666
You ready?
- Yes, sir.

40:18.666 --> 40:25.548
<i>♪ ♪</i>

40:34.766 --> 40:37.393
- All right, Chad.
These are amazingly sharp.

40:37.393 --> 40:40.647
Each one of those cuts
is beautiful and clean.

40:40.647 --> 40:42.649
They're very light, very fast.

40:42.649 --> 40:45.944
I think you did a beautiful job.
These are very nice weapons.

40:45.944 --> 40:48.488
- Thank you.

40:48.488 --> 40:50.782
- Bladesmiths, what started
as a round one

40:50.782 --> 40:52.617
nuts and bolts challenge

40:52.617 --> 40:54.452
came down to these bagh nakh.

40:54.452 --> 40:57.705
Both of you have put in
an incredible amount of work.

40:57.705 --> 40:59.749
Unfortunately, in this arena
of competition,

40:59.749 --> 41:01.834
there can only be one
"Forged in Fire" champion.

41:01.834 --> 41:04.253
<i>♪ ♪</i>

41:04.253 --> 41:06.214
Chad, congratulations.

41:06.214 --> 41:08.341
You are our new
"Forged in Fire" champion.

41:08.341 --> 41:10.677
Good job.
Josh, unfortunately,

41:10.677 --> 41:12.679
your bagh nakh
did not make the cut.

41:12.679 --> 41:15.723
- Josh, you brought us a matched
pair of beautiful knives,

41:15.723 --> 41:17.767
very sharp and comfortable
in the hand.

41:17.767 --> 41:19.686
But unfortunately,
in the strength test,

41:19.686 --> 41:21.354
<i>yours took more damage.</i>

41:21.354 --> 41:22.480
And that's why
I have to let you go.

41:22.480 --> 41:24.107
- I understand.

41:24.107 --> 41:26.734
- Josh, please
surrender your weapons.

41:26.734 --> 41:29.362
<i>- I'm a little discouraged,</i>
<i>a little disappointed.</i>

41:29.362 --> 41:31.906
